  ('elementary-0489de64-moex-00492', 'elementary-0489de64', 'elementary-0489de64-moex-112-b3f42868', 'sub-elementary-0489de64-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '①Incontrast ②Incomparison ③Infact ④Insummary', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:29:59+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "ea35e40f9519", "answer_pdf_sha1": "d51770cddb1b", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112010", "c": "511", "s": "0102", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "公民與英文", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 50, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["incomplete_options"], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "交通行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-0489de64-moex-00493', 'elementary-0489de64', 'elementary-0489de64-moex-112-34c7f7f6', 'sub-elementary-0489de64-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '假設你有一位朋友，他不被上司理解，不受同事接納，而你想要寫一段文字鼓勵他堅定地走 自己的路，不被他人影響，追尋自我價值。下列選項，最適當的是：', '["將自己與對方的看法聯結起來，一定要贏過對方才行", "過度誇耀自己的優點，是擔心身邊沒有人會認同自己", "無法接納自我的人容易將他人設為假想敵，用貶抑他人來獲得自信", "真正的自由是不在意他人的評價，不怕被人討厭，貫徹自己的想法"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:30:00+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "956a0c9fbe15", "answer_pdf_sha1": "1a6f54ad7459", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112010", "c": "511", "s": "0101", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "國文", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 1, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "交通行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-0489de64-moex-00494', 'elementary-0489de64', 'elementary-0489de64-moex-112-34c7f7f6', 'sub-elementary-0489de64-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列文句「」中的成語，何者使用最恰當？', '["老師工作時應該「聲色俱厲」，為學生夙夜匪懈", "感謝您大駕光臨，令寒舍「深居簡出」，小弟深感榮幸", "想當年這裡一片荒蕪，全賴前輩們「篳路藍縷」，才能欣欣向榮", "公司高層每日「披肝瀝膽」，你初來乍到要多加提防，免遭陷害"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:30:00+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "956a0c9fbe15", "answer_pdf_sha1": "1a6f54ad7459", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112010", "c": "511", "s": "0101", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "國文", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 2, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "交通行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-0489de64-moex-00495', 'elementary-0489de64', 'elementary-0489de64-moex-112-34c7f7f6', 'sub-elementary-0489de64-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列文句「」中的成語，何者使用正確？', '["他最近正在減重，本著「虛懷若谷」的意志力，吃得很節制", "當鳳凰花開季節，就是同學們要互道珍重、「分庭抗禮」的時候", "公司財務面臨危機，幸好老闆決定轉賣閒置廠房，堪稱「見異思遷」", "人應該要學習負責，這位母親「李代桃僵」，為女兒頂罪，反而害了她"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:30:00+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "956a0c9fbe15", "answer_pdf_sha1": "1a6f54ad7459", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112010", "c": "511", "s": "0101", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "國文", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 3, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "交通行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-0489de64-moex-00496', 'elementary-0489de64', 'elementary-0489de64-moex-112-34c7f7f6', 'sub-elementary-0489de64-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列文句「」內的詞語，用法錯誤的選項是：', '["他「逢人說項」，到處吹噓自己的勇猛", "他向來循規蹈矩，不會做出「雞鳴狗盜」的勾當", "經過此番激烈的砲戰，從此敵人不敢再「越雷池一步」", "李安拍了很多好片，獲獎無數，是導演行業的「個中翹楚」"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:30:00+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "956a0c9fbe15", "answer_pdf_sha1": "1a6f54ad7459", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112010", "c": "511", "s": "0101", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "國文", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 4, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "交通行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-0489de64-moex-00497', 'elementary-0489de64', 'elementary-0489de64-moex-112-34c7f7f6', 'sub-elementary-0489de64-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列文句「」中的成語，何者使用錯誤？', '["警方接到報案趕到現場，匪徒早已「杳如黃鶴」，不見蹤影", "這項工程最終靠著大家「任勞任怨」、努力不懈，才得以完成", "王教授的演講十分精彩，全場人士聽得「津津有味」，讚嘆不已", "我們公司非常嚴格，對任何流程的監控都小心翼翼，「瑕不掩瑜」"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:30:00+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "956a0c9fbe15", "answer_pdf_sha1": "1a6f54ad7459", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112010", "c": "511", "s": "0101", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "國文", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 5, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "交通行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-0489de64-moex-00498', 'elementary-0489de64', 'elementary-0489de64-moex-112-34c7f7f6', 'sub-elementary-0489de64-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列選項，何者最適宜「醫界」使用？', '["功著杏林", "利惠人群", "大業千秋", "福國利民"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:30:00+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "956a0c9fbe15", "answer_pdf_sha1": "1a6f54ad7459", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112010", "c": "511", "s": "0101", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "國文", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 6, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "交通行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-0489de64-moex-00499', 'elementary-0489de64', 'elementary-0489de64-moex-112-34c7f7f6', 'sub-elementary-0489de64-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列選項中的題辭與使用場合搭配，何者正確？', '["畢業：學無止境", "女喪：孟母遺風", "退休：德業長昭", "遷居：名山事業"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:30:00+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "956a0c9fbe15", "answer_pdf_sha1": "1a6f54ad7459", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112010", "c": "511", "s": "0101", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "國文", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 7, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "交通行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-0489de64-moex-00500', 'elementary-0489de64', 'elementary-0489de64-moex-112-34c7f7f6', 'sub-elementary-0489de64-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列文句「」中的成語，何者使用正確？', '["人事變化無常，不禁令人生起「樹猶如此」的慨嘆", "時逢春季，陽明山處處「蕙質蘭心」，吸引民眾駐足", "彎月高懸天際，「送眼流眉」的姿態，美得令人屏息", "跨年人潮眾多，一時之間「擢髮難數」，捷運只好加開班次"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:30:00+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "956a0c9fbe15", "answer_pdf_sha1": "1a6f54ad7459", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112010", "c": "511", "s": "0101", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "國文", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 8, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "交通行政"}'::jsonb, NULL)
